OL,3,CNew blood test can predict if breast
OL,4,Ccancer will come back
OL,6,FA new "ultra-sensitive" blood test can
OL,7,Fpredict if breast cancer will come
OL,8,Fback, years before it shows up on
OL,9,Fscans.
OL,11,FIt means treatment for the disease can
OL,12,Fstart before it becomes incurable.
OL,14,FThe test can pick up traces of a
OL,15,Ftumour's DNA ahead of a full relapse,
OL,16,Fwhen it is much harder to treat.
OL,18,FIt was found to be 100% accurate at
OL,19,Fpredicting which patients would see
OL,20,Ftheir cancer come back.
