OL,3,CNew blood test can predict if breast
OL,4,Ccancer will come back
OL,6,FThe "liquid biopsy" uses whole genome
OL,7,Fsequencing to look for genetic faults
OL,8,Fin a patient's DNA, which can be a
OL,9,Fsign of cancer.
OL,11,FA team of researchers from the
OL,12,FInstitute of Cancer Research (ICR),
OL,13,FLondon, conducted the trial on 78
OL,14,Fpatients with different types of early
OL,15,Fbreast cancer.
