OL,3,CNew blood test can predict if breast
OL,4,Ccancer will come back
OL,6,FLead researcher Dr Isaac Garcia-
OL,7,FMurillas said: "Breast cancer cells
OL,8,Fcan remain in the body after surgery
OL,9,Fand other treatments, but there can be
OL,10,Fso few of these cells that they are
OL,11,Fundetectable on follow-up scans.
OL,13,F"These cells can cause breast cancer
OL,14,Fpatients to relapse many years after
OL,15,Ftheir initial treatment.
OL,17,F"Ultra-sensitive blood tests could
OL,18,Foffer a better approach for the long-
OL,19,Fterm monitoring of patients whose
OL,20,Fcancer is at high risk of returning."
