OL,3,CNew blood test can predict if breast
OL,4,Ccancer will come back
OL,6,FThe test looks for 1,800 mutations in
OL,7,Fthe blood which are released by cancer
OL,8,Fcells, known as circulating tumour DNA
OL,9,F(ctDNA).
OL,11,FIt successfully found this ctDNA in 11
OL,12,Fwoman who all went on to see their
OL,13,Fcancer return. None of the other women
OL,14,Frelapsed.
OL,16,FDr Garcia-Murillas added: "Most
OL,17,Fpersonalised liquid biopsies currently
OL,18,Fuse whole exome sequencing to identify
OL,19,Fmutations.
