OL,3,CNew blood test can predict if breast
OL,4,Ccancer will come back
OL,6,F"But this approach goes one step
OL,7,Ffurther and uses whole genome
OL,8,Fsequencing to identify up to 1,800
OL,9,Fmutations in a patient's tumour DNA
OL,10,Fthat could uniquely identify
OL,11,Frecurrence of the patient's cancer
OL,12,Ffrom a blood sample.
OL,14,F"A more sensitive test is very
OL,15,Fimportant for this group of early
OL,16,Fbreast cancer patients as they tend to
OL,17,Fhave a very low amount of cancer DNA
OL,18,Fin their blood.
