OL,3,CNew blood test can predict if breast
OL,4,Ccancer will come back
OL,6,F"This proof-of-principle retrospective
OL,7,Fstudy lays the groundwork for better
OL,8,Fpost-treatment monitoring and
OL,9,Fpotentially life-extending treatment
OL,10,Fin patients."
OL,12,FOn average, the blood test detected
OL,13,Fcancer 15 months before symptoms
OL,14,Fappeared or it showed up on scans.
OL,16,FThe earliest was 41 months before a
OL,17,Fscan confirmed the diagnosis,
OL,18,Faccording to the results presented at
OL,19,Fthe American Society of Clinical
OL,20,FOncology conference in Chicago.
